      "body" : "I'm kind of inclined to say that we should just remove all the timestamps in messages.  It would be a lot cleaner then the conditional printfs in the patch.  If timestamps are off we could occasionally write markers in the log (E.g. once an hour, and at startup and shutdown).\n\n(I would just say we should enable timestamps alwaysÃ¢ÂÂ but I wouldn't want to make it more attractive for people to compromise bitcoin nodes in order to track the propagation of transactions)",
